 "html": "<div>\n<h3><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-5713 size-full\" src=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/1-1.png\" alt=\"Mosterdsous\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/1-1.png 640w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-300x300.png 300w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-100x100.png 100w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-600x600.png 600w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-150x150.png 150w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-530x530.png 530w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-500x500.png 500w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-380x380.png 380w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"></h3>\n<h3>Bestanddele</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>4 Eiers</li>\n<li>190 ml Asyn</li>\n<li>2 ml sout</li>\n<li>135 ml  (110g) suiker</li>\n<li>40 ml mosterdpoeier</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><b>Metode</b></h3>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ol>\n<li>Klits alles saam in ’n glasmengbak met ’n ballonklitser.</li>\n<li>Tap nou water in ’n gewone pot en sit die glasbak bo-op die pot met water.</li>\n<li>Kook die water en roer die inhoud in die glasbak gedurig. Al skuim die sous hou net aan roer.  Dit raak lekker dik en lyk amper soos mayonnaise.</li>\n</ol>\n<div><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-5714 size-full\" src=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/2-2.png\" alt=\"Mosterdsous\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/2-2.png 640w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-300x300.png 300w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-100x100.png 100w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-600x600.png 600w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-150x150.png 150w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-530x530.png 530w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-500x500.png 500w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-380x380.png 380w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"></div>\n<div>Plaas in die yskas om koud te raak.  Heerlik saam met vark, op toebroodjies of oor aartappelslaai.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5712 size-large\" src=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Mosterdsous\" width=\"530\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-768x1024.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-600x800.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-225x300.jpg 225w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-750x1000.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-380x507.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-760x1013.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-800x1067.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\"></div>\n</div>",
